;;;
;;;  Integrate Definite Integrals involving log and exp functions. The algorithm
;;;  are taken from the paper "Evaluation of CLasses of Definite Integrals ..."
;;;  by K.O.Geddes et. al.
;;;
;;;  1. CASE: Integrals generated by the Gamma function.
;;;
;;;    inf
;;;   /
;;;   [     w    m            s        - m - 1
